- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is another possible category as the paper deals with identifying and detecting potentially harmful accounts on social media. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is a possible category as the paper deals with classification algorithms for identifying pathogenic social media accounts. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also a possible category as the paper utilizes machine learning techniques for identifying and classifying pathogenic social media accounts.
